# Flow Configuration Guide

## Overview

This guide covers all aspects of Flow project configuration, from `flow.json` setup to FCL frontend integration. Use this as your central reference for configuring Flow projects across all environments.

## Quick Start

### Initialize Project
```bash
flow init
```

Creates:
- `flow.json` - Central configuration
- `emulator-account.pkey` - Emulator service account key
- `cadence/` directory structure

### Project Structure
```
my-project/
├── flow.json
├── emulator-account.pkey
├── cadence/
│   ├── contracts/
│   ├── scripts/
│   ├── transactions/
│   └── tests/
└── src/
    └── config/
        └── fcl-config.js
```

## flow.json Structure

### Core Sections

```json
{
  "networks": {},      // Network endpoints
  "accounts": {},      // Named accounts with keys
  "contracts": {},     // Contract sources and aliases
  "dependencies": {},  // External contract dependencies
  "deployments": {},   // Deployment targets
  "emulators": {}     // Custom emulator settings (optional)
}
```

### Networks Configuration

#### Basic Setup
```json
"networks": {
  "emulator": "127.0.0.1:3569",
  "testnet": "access.devnet.nodes.onflow.org:9000",
  "mainnet": "access.mainnet.nodes.onflow.org:9000"
}
```

#### Custom Networks
```json
"networks": {
  "emulator": "127.0.0.1:3569",
  "local-testnet": "127.0.0.1:3569",
  "testnet": "access.devnet.nodes.onflow.org:9000",
  "staging": {
    "host": "access-001.devnet30.nodes.onflow.org:9001",
    "key": "ba69f7d2e82b9edf..."
  }
}
```

### Accounts Configuration

#### Recommended: File-Based Keys
```json
"accounts": {
  "emulator-account": {
    "address": "f8d6e0586b0a20c7",
    "key": {
      "type": "file",
      "location": "emulator-account.pkey"
    }
  },
  "testnet-deployer": {
    "address": "544ad93e4effc077",
    "key": {
      "type": "file",
      "location": "testnet-deployer.pkey"
    }
  }
}
```

#### Environment Variables (Production)
```json
"accounts": {
  "mainnet-account": {
    "address": "1234567890abcdef",
    "key": "${FLOW_MAINNET_PRIVATE_KEY}"
  }
}
```

#### Account Best Practices
- ✅ Use file-based keys for security
- ✅ Never commit private keys to version control
- ✅ Verify account names match exactly (no typos)
- ✅ Ensure addresses match actual on-chain addresses
- ✅ Use environment variables for production keys

### Contracts Configuration

#### Basic Contract Setup
```json
"contracts": {
  "MyContract": {
    "source": "./cadence/contracts/MyContract.cdc",
    "aliases": {
      "emulator": "f8d6e0586b0a20c7",
      "testnet": "544ad93e4effc077"
