## Quick Reference

### Essential Commands
```bash
flow init                    # Initialize project
flow emulator                # Start emulator
flow project deploy          # Deploy contracts
flow config validate         # Validate configuration
flow test                    # Run tests
flow dependencies install    # Install dependencies
```

### Network Switching
```bash
flow config set env emulator
flow config set env testnet
flow config set env mainnet
```

### Common Paths
```
Storage: /storage/MyResource
Public: /public/MyCapability
Private: /private/MyCapability
```

